            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 2 月 22 日消息，发布两个多月后，三星 Galaxy Book 4 系列笔记本电脑已准备好在全球上市，包括 Galaxy Book 4 360、Galaxy Book 4 Pro、Galaxy Book 4 Pro 360 和 Galaxy Book 4 Ultra 四款机型。</p><p>从 2 月 26 日起，三星 Galaxy Book 4 系列将在全球市场上市（至少 Book 4 Pro、Book 4 Pro 360 和 Book 4 Ultra 会上市），目前&nbsp; Book 4 360 似乎仅限于印度等地区。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="545" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/2/e2a584be-0f7f-475a-a233-bb03fe99cd91.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="三星 Galaxy Book 4 笔记本电脑将于 2 月 26 日全球发售" width="1024" /></p><p>IT之家汇总四款产品规格如下：</p><table><tbody><tr class="firstRow"><td colspan="2" width="1000">Galaxy Book4 Ultra (16-inch)</td></tr><tr><td width="123">尺寸</td><td width="877">355.4 x 250.4 x 16.5mm</td></tr><tr><td width="123">重量</td><td width="877">1.86kg</td></tr><tr><td width="123">系统</td><td width="877"><a class="s_tag" href="https://win11.ithome.com/" target="_blank">Windows 11</a>&nbsp;家庭版</td></tr><tr><td width="123">屏幕</td><td width="877">16-inch, 16:10 Touch AMOLED, WQXGA+ (2880×1800),&nbsp;400nits, 48~120Hz VRR, 120% DCI-P3 颜色 volume</td></tr><tr><td width="123">处理器</td><td width="877">Intel&nbsp;Core&nbsp;Ultra 9 / Core<sup>™</sup>&nbsp;Ultra 7 (Intel&nbsp;Evo&nbsp;Edition)</td></tr><tr><td width="123">图形</td><td width="877">NVIDIA&nbsp;GeForce RTX<sup>™</sup>&nbsp;4070 Laptop GPU 8GB GDDR6<br />NVIDIA&nbsp;GeForce RTX<sup>™</sup>&nbsp;4050 Laptop GPU 6GB GDDR6</td></tr><tr><td width="123">网络</td><td width="877">Wi-Fi 6E, 802.11 ax 2×2, Bluetooth v5.3</td></tr><tr><td width="123">颜色</td><td width="877">Moonstone Gray</td></tr><tr><td width="123">内存</td><td width="877">16GB / 32GB / 64GB (LPDDR5X)</td></tr><tr><td width="123">内置存储</td><td width="877">512GB / 1TB / 2TB SSD (PCle), Expansion Slot</td></tr><tr><td width="123">相机</td><td width="877">2M (1080p FHD)</td></tr><tr><td width="123">麦克风<br /></td><td width="877">Studio-quality Dual Microphones / AKG Quad speakers&nbsp;(Woofer Max 5Wx2, Tweeter 2Wx2), Dolby Atmos</td></tr><tr><td width="123">键盘</td><td width="877">Pro keyboard with Numeric key (Backlit keyboard)</td></tr><tr><td width="123">电池</td><td width="877">76Wh (Typical)</td></tr><tr><td width="123">充电</td><td width="877">140W USB Type-C Adapter</td></tr><tr><td width="123">端口</td><td width="877">Thunderbolt&nbsp;4 (2), USB Type-A, HDMI 2.1 port (Supports 8K@60, 5K@120), Micro SD, Headphone / Microphone</td></tr></tbody></table><table><tbody><tr class="firstRow"><td colspan="2" width="1000">Galaxy Book4 Pro 360 (16-inch)</td></tr><tr><td width="123">尺寸</td><td width="877">355.4 x 252.2 x 12.8mm</td></tr><tr><td width="123">重量</td><td width="877">1.66kg</td></tr><tr><td width="123">系统</td><td width="877">Windows 11 Home</td></tr><tr><td width="123">屏幕</td><td width="877">16-inch, 16:10 Touch AMOLED, WQXGA+ (2880×1800), 400nits, 48~120Hz VRR, 120% DCI-P3 颜色 volume</td></tr><tr><td width="123">处理器</td><td width="877">Intel<sup>®</sup>&nbsp;Core<sup>™</sup>&nbsp;Ultra 7 /&nbsp; Core<sup>™</sup>&nbsp;Ultra 5 (Intel<sup>®</sup>&nbsp;Evo<sup>™</sup>&nbsp;Edition)</td></tr><tr><td width="123">图形</td><td width="877">Intel<sup>®</sup>&nbsp;Arc<sup>™</sup>&nbsp;Graphics (Shared)</td></tr><tr><td width="123">网络</td><td width="877">Wi-Fi 6E, 802.11 ax 2×2, Bluetooth v5.3</td></tr><tr><td width="123">颜色</td><td width="877">Moonstone Gray, Platinum Silver</td></tr><tr><td width="123">内存</td><td width="877">16GB / 32GB (LPDDR5X)</td></tr><tr><td width="123">存储</td><td width="877">512GB / 1TB SSD (PCIe)</td></tr><tr><td width="123">相机</td><td width="877">2M (1080p FHD)</td></tr><tr><td width="123">麦克风 / 扬声器</td><td width="877">Studio-quality Dual Microphones / AKG Quad speakers (Woofer Max 5Wx2, Tweeter 2Wx2), Dolby Atmos<sup>®</sup></td></tr><tr><td width="123">键盘</td><td width="877">Pro keyboard with Numeric key (Backlit keyboard)</td></tr><tr><td width="123">手写笔</td><td width="877">S Pen (In-box)</td></tr><tr><td width="123">电池</