r><td width="123">相机</td><td colspan="2" width="877">2M (1080p FHD)</td><td width="1"><br /></td></tr><tr><td width="123">麦克风 / 扬声器</td><td colspan="2" width="877">Studio-quality Dual Microphones / AKG Quad speakers (Woofer Max 5Wx2, Tweeter 2Wx2), Dolby Atmos<sup>®</sup></td><td width="1"><br /></td></tr><tr><td width="123">键盘</td><td width="438.5">Pro keyboard (Backlit keyboard)</td><td colspan="2" width="438.5">Pro keyboard with Numeric key (Backlit keyboard)</td></tr><tr><td width="123">电池</td><td width="438.5">63Wh (Typical)</td><td colspan="2" width="438.5">76Wh (Typical)</td></tr><tr><td width="123">充电</td><td colspan="2" width="877">65W USB Type-C Adapter</td><td width="1"><br /></td></tr><tr><td width="123">端口</td><td colspan="2" width="877">Thunderbolt<sup>™</sup>&nbsp;4 (2), USB Type-A, HDMI 2.1 port (Supports 8K@60, 5K@120), Micro SD, Headphone / Microphone</td><td colspan="1" width="877"><br /></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Galaxy Book 4 Pro / Pro 360 / Ultra 型号搭载 Dynamic AMOLED 触控屏幕，拥有 3K 分辨率 120Hz 刷新率，具备“Vision Booster”技术，可根据外部光线调整笔记本色温、亮度及对比度。</p><p>此外，Galaxy Book 4 系列笔记本还将首次搭载三星 Knox 安全芯片，号称可以提供更强大的安全性能。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="545" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/c03b5a52-7a12-46b2-b5dc-e27d2267c423.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="三星 Galaxy Book 4 笔记本电脑将于 2 月 26 日全球发售" width="1024" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="562" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/2234ae60-570c-4861-aeaf-d9ed56717514.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="三星 Galaxy Book 4 笔记本电脑将于 2 月 26 日全球发售" width="1024" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="601" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/bdfc0174-4767-48ed-bf14-1d47399ced60.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="三星 Galaxy Book 4 笔记本电脑将于 2 月 26 日全球发售" width="1024" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1230" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/991b9eb1-34f3-4679-93b2-415525de