            <title>4999 元起，小米 Redmi Book Pro 14/16 2024 笔记本发布：Ultra 5/7 处理器，接入澎湃智联</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/751/490.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/751/490.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
